'''The Indexer''' was a member of a colony of [[Unidentified boneless species|boneless beings]] on [[Chalcedon/Legends|Chalcedon]]. In 14 ABY, Princess [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia]] (disguised as the [[Bounty hunter/Legends|bounty hunter]] [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Lelila]]) and [[Rillao]] tried to get information from him about [[Firrerreo/Legends|Firrerreo]] sold in the [[Slavery/Legends|slave trade]]. He charged them for sorting through all the trade information he had, only to tell them that there were no public records of that Firrerreo had ever been sold as a slave. He suggested that private slave selling was rumored to take place in the [[Crseih Station|Asylum Station]], and asked them to confirm the rumor, as it would mean that Chalcedon had a rival in the slave trade.

